extends template.pug

block variables
    -var title = 'Register'

block main-content
    h4 Please select plan type:
    form.pt-2#full-form(action="/register/full", method="get").row.mb-2
        div.col-1.text-center
            button.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm(type="submit") Full
        div#full-plan-description.col-11 Purges the bot when detected, but required channel moderator permission.
    form.pt-2#strict-form(action="/register/strict", method="get").row.mb-2
        div.col-1.text-center
            button.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm(type="submit") Full
        div#strict-plan-description.col-11 Bans the bot when detected, instead of purging. Note: by using this plan you may risk my anti-bot accidentally banning the wrong people.
    form#lite-form(action="/register/lite", method="get").row.mb-2
        div.col-1.text-center
            button.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm(type="submit") Lite
        div#lite-plan-description.col-11 Doesn't require channel moderator permissions, but doesn't actually take action against the bot, only comments that "it's a bot". Used to test the functionality of this anti-bot bot.
